### BITWIN Security Module REST API Tests
@baseUrl = http://localhost:2000

---
### 1. Initiate OAuth Login
### Open this URL in your browser to authenticate.
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/google

### 2. Check Auth Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/status

---
### 3. Gmail Inbox Analysis
### Fetch latest 5 emails (combined Inbox + Spam) with AI reasoning.
GET {{baseUrl}}/gmail/latest

### 4. Start Real-time Monitoring
### Starts polling Gmail every 20s.
POST {{baseUrl}}/gmail/start-watch

### 5. Stop Real-time Monitoring
POST {{baseUrl}}/gmail/stop-watch

---
### 6. Website URL Detector
### Analyze a suspicious URL for phishing or malicious patterns.
POST {{baseUrl}}/url
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "url": "https://secure-login-bank-verify-account.com/login"
}

### 7. Website URL Detector (Safe Example)
POST {{baseUrl}}/url
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "url": "https://www.google.com"
}

---
### 8. Deepfake Photo Detector
### Upload an image to check for AI generation/manipulation.
POST {{baseUrl}}/predict-image
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="test.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

(Binary data would go here)
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

---
### 9. Direct Text Analysis
### Analyze a raw email body or text snippet manually.
POST {{baseUrl}}/predict
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "emailBody": "Urgent: Your account has been suspended. Click here to login: http://bit.ly/fake-link"
}
